trans-unit.source: Represents information used to obtain an issued token from a security token service.
trans-unit.target: Representerer informasjon som brukes til å hente et utstedt token fra en sikkerhetstokentjenesten.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a Boolean that specifies whether issued tokens are to be cached by the channel.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en boolsk verdi som angir om utstedte token skal hurtigbufres av kanalen.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if tokens are to be cached; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis tokener skal hurtigbufres; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default value is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Attempt to <xref uid="langword_csharp_set" name="set" href=""></xref> a read-only credential.
trans-unit.target: Forsøk på å <xref uid="langword_csharp_set" name="set" href=""> </xref> skrivebeskyttet legitimasjon.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the default value of <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Security.SecurityKeyEntropyMode"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir standardverdien for <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Security.SecurityKeyEntropyMode"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: When the client does WS-Trust exchange with the Security Token Service to obtain the issued token, it sometimes must exchange key entropy with the Security Token Service to arrive at a shared symmetric key.
trans-unit.target: Når klienten utfører WS-Trust exchange med sikkerhetstokentjenesten ikke hente utstedt token, må den noen ganger exchange key entropy med sikkerhetstokentjenesten ankommer en delt symmetrisk nøkkel.

trans-unit.source: The Security Token Service typically specifies the entropy exchange mechanism to use in its binding.
trans-unit.target: Sikkerhetstokentjenesten angir vanligvis entropy exchange mekanisme for bruk i bindingen.

trans-unit.source: If no such mechanism is specified in the Security Token Service's binding, the `DefaultKeyEntropyMode` value is used to exchange entropy with the Security Token Service.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ingen slike mekanisme er angitt i Sikkerhetstokentjenestens binding av `DefaultKeyEntropyMode` verdien brukes til exchange entropy med sikkerhetstokentjenesten.

trans-unit.source: The value of <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Security.SecurityKeyEntropyMode"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Security.SecurityKeyEntropyMode"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Security.SecurityKeyEntropyMode"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Security.SecurityKeyEntropyMode"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: An attempt was made to <xref uid="langword_csharp_set" name="set" href=""></xref> a read-only credential.
trans-unit.target: Forsøk på å <xref uid="langword_csharp_set" name="set" href=""> </xref> skrivebeskyttet legitimasjon.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the renewal threshold percentage for issued tokens.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir fornyelse terskelverdien for utstedte token.

trans-unit.source: The client caches issued tokens and when a cached issued token is going to expire in the near future, the client automatically gets a fresh issued token from the Security Token Service.
trans-unit.target: Klient-buffere utstedt token, og når et hurtigbufret utstedt token skal utløpe i nær fremtid, får klienten automatisk en ny utstedt token fra sikkerhetstokentjenesten.

trans-unit.source: The value of this property determines what percentage of the cached issued token's validity period must be over before getting a fresh issued token.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for denne egenskapen bestemmer hvilken prosent av den bufrede utstedt token gyldighetsperiode må være før du får et nytt utstedt token.

trans-unit.source: For example, if this property's value is 60, and the client gets an issued token that is valid for 100 minutes, it reuses the cached issued token for 60 minutes, after which it gets a fresh issued token from the Security Token Service.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis denne egenskapens verdi er 60, og klienten henter en utstedte token som er gyldig for 100 minutter, brukes på nytt bufret utstedt token for 60 minutter, etter som henter den et nytt utstedt token fra sikkerhetstokentjenesten.

trans-unit.source: The renewal threshold percentage for issued tokens.
trans-unit.target: Fornyelse terskelverdien for utstedte token.

trans-unit.source: The default value is 60.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er 60.

trans-unit.source: An attempt was made to <xref uid="langword_csharp_set" name="set" href=""></xref> a read-only credential.
trans-unit.target: Forsøk på å <xref uid="langword_csharp_set" name="set" href=""> </xref> skrivebeskyttet legitimasjon.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of issuer channel behaviors.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling av utsteder kanal virkemåter.

trans-unit.source: The dictionary keys are the URIs of the Security Token Services that the client wants to communicate with.
trans-unit.target: Nøklene ordliste er URIer for sikkerhet Token-tjenester som klienten ønsker å kommunisere med.

trans-unit.source: The entry for each URI is a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.KeyedByTypeCollection%601> of the endpoint behaviors that the application uses in the channels created by [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] to get the issued tokens from the Security Token Services.
trans-unit.target: Oppføringen for hver URI er en <xref:System.Collections.Generic.KeyedByTypeCollection%601>av endepunkt som bruker programmet i kanaler opprettet av [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] å hente utstedte tokener fra sikkerhet Token-tjenestene.</xref:System.Collections.Generic.KeyedByTypeCollection%601>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602> of <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IEndpointBehavior>s.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602> av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IEndpointBehavior>s.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IEndpointBehavior>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the address of the local issuer.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir adressen til den lokale utstederen.

trans-unit.source: When obtaining an issued token from a Security Token Service, the client application must be configured with the address of the Security Token Service.
trans-unit.target: Når slik får du et utstedt token fra en sikkerhetstokentjenesten, må være konfigurert klientprogrammet med postadressen sikkerhetstokentjenesten.

trans-unit.source: This information can be specified by the target service in its security policy.
trans-unit.target: Denne informasjonen kan være angitt av målservicen i sikkerhetspolicyen.

trans-unit.source: In case the target service does not specify this information in its security policy, the client's [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] channel uses the `LocalIssuerAddress` as the address of the Security Token Service from which to obtain the issued token.
trans-unit.target: I tilfelle målservicen ikke angir denne informasjonen i sikkerhetspolicyen, klientens [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] kanalen bruker den `LocalIssuerAddress` som adressen til sikkerhetstokentjenesten som du kan hente utstedt token.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress> of the local issuer.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress>for lokale utstederen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress>

trans-unit.source: An attempt was made to <xref uid="langword_csharp_set" name="set" href=""></xref> a read-only credential.
trans-unit.target: Forsøk på å <xref uid="langword_csharp_set" name="set" href=""> </xref> skrivebeskyttet legitimasjon.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the binding of the local issuer.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir bindingen for den lokale utstederen.

trans-unit.source: When obtaining an issued token from a Security Token Service, the client application must be configured with the binding to use to communicate with the Security Token Service.
trans-unit.target: Når slik får du et utstedt token fra en sikkerhetstokentjenesten, må være konfigurert klientprogrammet med bindingen som skal brukes til å kommunisere med sikkerhetstokentjenesten.

trans-unit.source: In case the target service does not specify information about the Security Token Service in its security policy, the client's [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] channel uses the LocalIssuerBinding as the binding to use to communicate with the Security Token Service.
trans-unit.target: I tilfelle målservicen ikke angi informasjon om sikkerhetstokentjenesten i sikkerhetspolicyen, klientens [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] kanal bruker LocalIssuerBinding som bindingen skal brukes til å kommunisere med sikkerhetstokentjenesten.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Binding> of the local issuer.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Binding>for lokale utstederen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Binding>

trans-unit.source: An attempt was made to <xref uid="langword_csharp_set" name="set" href=""></xref> a read-only credential.
trans-unit.target: Forsøk på å <xref uid="langword_csharp_set" name="set" href=""> </xref> skrivebeskyttet legitimasjon.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of local issuer channel behaviors.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling av lokale utsteder kanal virkemåter.

trans-unit.source: This is a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.KeyedByTypeCollection%601> of the endpoint behaviors that the application uses in the channels created by [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] to get the issued tokens from the local Security Token Service.
trans-unit.target: Dette er en <xref:System.Collections.Generic.KeyedByTypeCollection%601>av endepunkt som bruker programmet i kanaler opprettet av [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] ikke hente utstedte token fra lokale sikkerhetstokentjenesten.</xref:System.Collections.Generic.KeyedByTypeCollection%601>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.KeyedByTypeCollection%601> of <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IEndpointBehavior>s.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.Generic.KeyedByTypeCollection%601> av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IEndpointBehavior>s.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IEndpointBehavior>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the maximum caching time for an issued token.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir maksimalt hurtigbufring lenge et utstedt token.

trans-unit.source: By default, issued tokens obtained from the Security Token Service are cached by the [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] client channel.
trans-unit.target: Som standard hurtigbufres utstedte token hentet fra sikkerhetstokentjenesten av den [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] klienten kanal.

trans-unit.source: This property enables the application to specify the maximum time that the channel caches the issued token.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen kan programmet til å angi hvor lenge kanalen bufrer utstedt token.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.TimeSpan> that represents the maximum caching time for an issued token.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.TimeSpan>som representerer maksimumsverdien hurtigbufring lenge et utstedt token.</xref:System.TimeSpan>

trans-unit.source: The default value is <xref:System.TimeSpan>.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er <xref:System.TimeSpan>.</xref:System.TimeSpan>

trans-unit.source: The value of <xref uid="langword_csharp_set" name="set" href=""></xref> is less than zero.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for <xref uid="langword_csharp_set" name="set" href=""> </xref> er mindre enn null.

trans-unit.source: An attempt was made to <xref uid="langword_csharp_set" name="set" href=""></xref> a read-only credential.
trans-unit.target: Forsøk på å <xref uid="langword_csharp_set" name="set" href=""> </xref> skrivebeskyttet legitimasjon.
